[+] We’ve added access to the Anthem Medicaid app for our Kentucky members – Welcome!
[+] Improvement of the ID Card experience for all states, providing more stable card images.
[+] Members now have the option to translate the app into Spanish. If you want to switch between English and Spanish, access the App Language from the info bubble on Login page, or from the “About App” menu if you are already logged in.
[+] Bug fixes

[+] Healthy Indiana Plan (HIP) members can now view their POWER Account status within the app, via the Menu (My Account, POWER Account Overview).

[+] HIP members who need to add a credit/bank card as a payment method for monthly bills can now use their phone's camera to easily and securely save their card account number within the app!
